quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  6,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  6,1,"tareef Allah ke liye hai jis ne zameen aur aasman banaye, roshni aur tarikhiyan peda kee phir bhi woh log jinhon ne dawat haq ko maan-ne se inkaar kar diya hai dosaron ko apne rab ka humsartehra rahay hain"
  6,2,"wohi hai jis ne tum ko matti se peda kya, phir tumahray liye zindagi ki aik muddat muqarrar kar di, aur aik doosri muddat aur bhi hai jwas ke haan tey shuda hai magar tum log ho ke shak mein parre hue ho"
  6,3,"wohi aik khuda asmano mein bhi hai aur zameen mein bhi, tumahray khulay aur chupay sab haal jaanta hai aur jo buraiee ya bhalai tum kamate ho is se khoob waaqif hai"
  6,4,logon ka haal yeh hai ke un ke rab ki nshanyon mein se koi nishani aisi nahi jo un ke samnay aayi ho aur unhon ne is se mun nah mourr liya ho
  6,5,"chunancha ab jo haq un ke paas aaya to usay bhi unhon ne jhutla diya acha, jis cheez ka woh ab taq mazaq uratay rahay hain anqareeb is ke mutaliq kuch khabrain inhen pohnchain gi"
  6,6,"kya unhon ne dekha nahi ke un se pehlay kitni aisi qomon ko hum halaak kar chuke hain jin ka apne apne zamana mein daur dora raha hai? unn ko hum ne zameen mein woh Iqtidaar bakhsha tha jo tumhe nahi bakhsha hai, un par hum ne aasman se khoob barishain barsaaen aur un ke neechay nhrin baha den, ( magar jab unhon ne kufran Nemat kya to ) aakhir-kaar hum ne un ke gunaaho ki Padaash mein inhen tabah kar diya aur un ki jagah dosray daur ki qomon ko uthaya"
  6,7,aePeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam agar hum tumahray oopar koi kaghaz mein likhi likhai kitaab bhi utaar dete aur log usay apne hathon se chhoo kar bhi dekh letay tab bhi jinhon ne haq ka inkaar kya hai woh yahi kehte ke yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai
  6,8,"kehte hain ke is nabi par koi farishta kyun nahi utaara gaya agar kahin hum ne farishta utaar diya hota to ab taq kabhi ka faisla ho chuka hota, phir inhen koi mohlat nah di jati"
  6,9,aur agar hum farishtay ko utaartay tab bhi usay insani shakal hi mein utaartay aur is terhan inhen usi shuba mein mubtala kar dete jis mein ab yeh mubtala hain
  6,10,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! tum se pehlay bhi bohat se Rasolo-n ka mazaq uraya ja chuka hai, magar un mazaq urane walon par aakhir-kaar wohi haqeeqat musallat ho kar rahi jis ka woh mazaq uratay thay"
  6,11,"inn se kaho, zara zameen mein chal phir kar dekho jhutlanay walon ka kya injaam howa hai"
  6,12,"un se pucho, asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai woh kis kaahe? kaho sab kuch Allah hi ka hai, is ne reham o karam ka Shewa apne oopar lazim kar liya hai ( isi liye woh nafarmanio-n aursarkasyun اpar tumhe jaldi se nahi pakar laita ), qayamat ke roz woh tum sab ko zaroor jama kere ga, yeh bilkul aik ghair mushtaba haqeeqat hai, magar jin logon ne apne aap ko khud tabahi ke khatray mein mubtala kar liya hai woh usay nahi mantay"
  6,13,"raat ke andheray aur din ke ujalay mein jo kuchtehra howa hai, sab Allah ka hai aur woh sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
  6,14,"kaho, Allah ko chore kar kya mein kisi aur ko apna sir parast bana lon? uss khuda ko chore kar jo zameen o aasman ka khaaliq hai aur jo rozi deta hai rozi laita nahi hai? kaho, mujhe to yahi hukum diya gaya hai ke sab se pehlay mein uss ke agay sir tasleem khham karoon ( aur takeed ki gayi hai ke koi shirk karta hai to kere ) to behar haal mushrikon mein shaamil nah ho"
  6,15,"kaho, agar mein apne rab ki nafarmani karoon to darta hon ke aik barray ( khofnaak ) din mujhe saza bhgtni parre gi"
  6,16,uss din jo saza se bach gaya is par Allah ne bara hi reham kya aur yahi numaya kamyabi hai
  6,17,"agar Allah tumhe kisi qisam ka nuqsaan p_hnchaye to is ke siwa koi nahi jo tumhe is nuqsaan se bacha sakay, aur agar woh tumhe kisi bhalai se behra mand kere to woh har cheez par Qadir hai"
  6,18,woh apne bundon par kaamil ikhtiyarat rakhta hai aur Dana aur bakhabar hai
  6,19,"un se pucho, kis ki gawahi sab se barh kar hai? kaho, mere aur tumahray darmain Allah gawah hai, aur yeh quran meri taraf ba zarea wahi bheja gaya hai taakay tumhe aur jis jis ko yeh puhanche, sab ko mutnabba kar dun kya waqai tum log yeh shahadat day satke ho ke Allah ke sath dosray khuda bhi hain? kaho, mein to is ki shahadat hargiz nahi day sakta kaho, khuda to wohi aik hai aur mein is shirk se qatee bezaar hon jis mein tum mubtala ho"
  6,20,jin logon ko hum ne kitaab di hai woh is baat ko is terhan ghair mushtaba tor par pehchante hain jaisay un ko apne beiton ke pehchanney mein koi ishtibaah paish nahi aata magar jinhon ne apne aap ko khud khasaray mein daal diya hai woh isay nahi mantay
  6,21,"aur uss shakhs se barh kar zalim kon hoga jo Allah par jhoota bohtan lagaye, ya Allah ki nshanyon kojhutla-ay? yaqeenan aisay zalim kabhi Falah nahi pa satke"
  6,22,jis roz hum un sab ko akhatta karen ge aur mushrikon se poucheen ge ke ab woh tumahray tehra-ay hue shareek kahan hain jin ko tum apna khuda samajte thay
  6,23,to woh iss ke siwa koi fitnah nah utha saken ge ke ( yeh jhoota bayan den ke ) ae hamaray aaqa! teri qasam hum hargiz mushriknah thay
  6,24,"dekho, uss waqt yeh kis terhan apne oopar aap jhoot gharein ge, aur wahan unn ke saaray banawati mabood gum ho jayen ge"
  6,25,"un mein se baaz log aisay hain jo kaan laga kar tumhari baat suntay hain magar haal yeh hai ke hum ne unn ke dilon par parday daal rakhay hain jin ki wajah se woh is ko kuch nahi samajte aur un ke kaanon mein gharani daal di hai ( ke sab kuch suneney par bhi kuch nahi suntay ) woh khuwa koi nishani dekh len, is par imaan laa kar nah den ge hadd yeh hai ke jab woh tumahray paas aa kar tum se jhagarte hain to un mein se jin logon ne inkaar ka faisla kar liya hai woh ( saari baatein suneney ke baad ) yahi kehte hain ke yeh aik daastaa’n Parinah ke siwa kuch nahi"
  6,26,woh is amar haq ko qubool karne se logon ko roktay hain aur khud bhi is se daur bhagtay hain ( woh samajte hain ke is harkat se woh tumhara kuch bigaar rahay hain ) halaank darasal woh khoo daal apni hi tabahi ka samaan kar rahay hain magar inhen is ka shaoor nahi hai
  6,27,kash tum is waqt un ki haalat dekh satke jab woh dozakh ke kinare kharray kiye jayen ge is waqt woh kahin ge ke kash koi soorat aisi ho ke hum duniya mein phir wapas beje jayen aur apne rab ki nshanyon ko nahjjhutlain aur imaan laane walon mein shaamil hon
  6,28,"Dur haqeeqat yeh ba t- woh mehez is wajah se kahin ge ke jis haqeeqat par unhon ne parda daal rakha tha woh is waqt be naqaab ho kar un ke samnay aa chuki hogi, warna agar inhen sabiq zindagi ki taraf wapas bheja jaye to phir wohi sab kuch karen jis se inhen mana kya gaya hai, woh to hain hi jhutay ( is liye apni is khwahish ke izhaar mein bhi jhoot hi se kaam len ge )"
  6,29,aaj yeh log kehte hain ke zindagi jo kuch bhi hai bas yahi duniya ki zindagi hai aur hum marnay ke baad hargiz dobarah nah uthaye jayen ge
  6,30,"kash woh manzar tum dekh sakuu jab yeh apne rab ke samnay kharray kiye jayen ge is waqt un ka rab un se pouchye ga"" kya yeh haqeeqat nahi hai ?"" yeh kahin ge"" haan ae hamaray rab! yeh haqeeqat hi hai"" woh farmaiye ga"" acha! to ab apne inkaar haqeeqat ki Padaash mein azaab ka maza chako """
  6,31,"nuqsaan mein par gay woh log jinhon ne Allah se apni mulaqaat ki ittila ko jhoot qarar diya jab achanak woh gharri aa jaye gi to yahi log kahin ge"" afsos! hum se is maamla mein kaisi taqseer hui"" aur inn ka haal yeh hoga ke apni pithon par apne gunaaho ka boojh lade hue hon ge dekho! kaisa bura boojh hai jo yeh utha rahay hain"
  6,32,"duniya ki zindagi to aik khail aur aik tamasha hai, haqeeqat mein akhirat hi ka maqam unn logon ke liye behtar hai jo zayan kaari se bachna chahtay hain, phir kya tum log aqal se kaam nah lau ge ?"
  6,33,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! hamein maloom hai ke jo baatein yeh log banatay hain un se tumhe ranj hota hai, lekin yeh log tumhe nahi jutlatay balkay yeh zalim darasal Allah ki ayaat ka inkaar kar rahay hain"
  6,34,"tum se pehlay bhi bohat se rasooljhutla-ay ja chuke hain, magar is tkzib par aur unn aziyatoon par jo inhen pohanchai gayeen, unhon ne sabr kya, yahan taq ke inhen hamari madad poanch gayi Allah ki baton ko badalny ki taaqat kisi mein nahi hai, aur pichlle Rasolo-n ke sath jo kuch paish aaya is ki khabrain tumhe poanch hi chuki hain"
  6,35,"taham agar un logon ki be rukhi tum se bardasht nahi hoti to agar tum mein kuch zor hai to zameen mein koi surang dhuundo ya aasman mein seerhi lagao aur un ke paas koi nishani laane ki koshish karo agar Allah chahta to un sab ko hadaayat par jama kar sakta tha, lehaza nadaan mat bano"
  6,36,"dawat haq par labaik wohi log kehte hain jo suneney walay hain, rahay murdy, to inhen to Allah bas qabron hi se uthaye ga aur phir woh ( is ki adalat mein paish honay ke liye ) wapas laaye jayen ge"
  6,37,"yeh log kehte hain ke iss nabi par is ke rab ki taraf se koi nishani kyun nahi utri? kaho, Allah nishani utaarnay ki poori qudrat rakhta hai, magar un mein se aksar log nadani mein mubtala hain"
  6,38,"zameen mein chalne walay kisi janwar aur howa mein paron se urrnay walay kisi parinday ko dekh lau, yeh sab tumhari hi terhan ki anwaa hain, hum ne un ki taqdeer ke noshte mein koi kasar nahi choari hai, phir yeh sab apne rab ki taraf samete jatay hain"
  6,39,"magar jo log hamari nshanyon ko jutlatay hain woh behray aur gungay hain, tarikeon mein parre hue hain Allah jisay chahta hai bhatka deta hai aur jisay chahta hai seedhay raste par laga deta hai"
  6,40,"un se kaho, zara ghhor kar ke batao, agar kabhi tum par Allah ki taraf se koi barri museebat aa jati hai ya aakhri gharri aa pahunchti hai to kya is waqt tum Allah ke siwa kisi aur ko pkarte ho? balow agar tum sachey ho"
  6,41,"a seen waqt tum Allah hi ko pkarte ho, phir agar woh chahta hai to is museebat ko tum par se taall deta hai aisay moqaon par tum apne tehra-ay hue sharikon ko bhool jatay ho"
  6,42,tum se pehlay bohat si qomon ki taraf hum ne rasool beje aur unn qomon ko masaaib o alaam mein mubtala kya taakay woh aajzi ke sath hamaray samnay jhuk jayen
  6,43,pas jab hamari taraf se un par sakhti aayi to kyun nah unhon ne aajzi ikhtiyar ki? magar un ke dil to aur sakht hogaye aur shetan ne un ko itminan dilaya ke jo kuch tum kar rahay ho khoob kar rahay ho
  6,44,"phir jab unhon ne is nasiyaat ko, jo inhen ki gayi thi, bhala diya to hum ne har terhan ki khushaaliyon ke darwazay un ke liye khol diye, yahan taq ke jab woh unn bakhshishon mein jo inhen ataa ki gayi theen khoob magan hogaye to achanak hum ne inhen pakar liya aur ab haal yeh tha ke woh har kher se mayoos thay"
  6,45,is terhan un logon ki jarr kaat kar rakh di gayi jinhon ne zulm kya tha aur tareef hai Allah rab alaalmin ke liye ( ke is ne un ki jarr kaat di )
  6,46,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho, kabhi tum ne yeh bhi socha ke agar Allah tumhari benaye aur samaat tum se chean le aur tumahray dilon par mohar kar day to Allah ke siwa aur kon sa khuda hai jo yeh quwaten tumhe wapas dlaskta ho? dekho, kis terhan hum baar baar apni nishanain un ke samnay paish karte hain aur phir yeh kis terhan un se nazar chura jatay hain"
  6,47,"kaho, kabhi tum ne socha ke agar Allah ki taraf se achanak ya alania tum par azaab aa jaye to kya zalim logon ke siwa koi aur halaak hoga ?"
  6,48,hum jo rasool bhaijtay hain isi liye to bhaijtay hain ke woh naik kirdaar logon ke liye khush khaberi dainay walay aur bad krdaron ke liye darane walay hon phir jo log un ki baat maan len aur apne tarz amal ki islaah kar len un ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nahi hai
  6,49,aur jo hamari ayaat kojjhutlainwoh apni nafarmanio-n ki Padaash mein saza bhagat kar rahen ge
  6,50,"a y Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho,"" mein tum se yeh nahi kehta ke mere paas Allah ke khazanay hain nah mein ghaib ka ilm rakhta hon, aur nah yeh kehta hon ke mein farishta hon mein to sirf uss wahi ki pairwi karta hon jo mujh par nazil ki jati hai"" phir un se pucho kya andha aur aankhon wala dono barabar ho saktay hain? kya tum ghhor nahi karte ?"
  6,51,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! tum is ( ilm wahi ) ke zareya se unn logon ko nasiyaat karo jo is baat ka khauf rakhtay hain ke apne rab ke samnay kabhi is haal mein paish kiye jayen ge ke uss ke siwa wahan koi ( aisa Zee Iqtidaar ) nah hoga jo un ka haami o madad gaar ho, ya un ki sifarish kere, shayad ke ( is nasiyaat se mutnabba ho kar ) woh khuda tarsi ki rawish ikhtiyar kar len"
  6,52,aur jo log apne rab ko raat din pkarte rehtay hain o ray is ki khushnodi ki talab mein lagey hue hain inhen apne se daur nah phenko unn ke hisaab mein se kisi cheez ka baar tum par nahi hai aur tumahray hisaab mein se kisi cheez ka baar unn par nahi is par bhi agar tum inhen daur phenko ge to zaalmon mein shumaar ho ge
  6,53,"darasal hum ne is terhan un logon mein se baaz ko baaz ke zareya se azmaish mein dala hai taakay woh aِnhin dekh kar kahin"" kya yeh hain woh log jin par hamaray darmain Allah ka fazl o karam howa hai ?"" haan! kya khuda apne shukar guzaar bundon ko inn se ziyada nahi jaanta hai ?"
  6,54,"jab tumahray paas woh log ayen jo hamari ayaat par imaan laatay hain to un se kaho"" tum par salamti hai tumahray rab ne reham o karam ka Shewa apne oopar lazim kar liya hai yeh is ka reham o karam hi hai ke agar tum mein se koi nadani ke sath kisi buraiee ka irtikaab kar betha ho phir is ke baad tauba kere aur islaah kar le to woh ussay maaf kar deta hai aur narmi se kaam laita hai """
  6,55,aur is terhan hum apni nishanain khol khol kar paish karte hain taakay mujrimon ki raah bilkul numaya ho jaye
  6,56,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! inn se kaho ke tum log Allah ke siwa jin dosaron ko pkarte ho unn ki bandagi karne se mujhe mana kya gaya hai kaho, mein tumhari khwahisaat ki pairwi nahi karoon ga, agar mein ne aisa kya to gumraah ho gaya, raah raast panay walon mein se nah raha"
  6,57,"kaho, mein apne rab ki taraf se aik Daleel roshan par qaim hon aur tum ne usay jhutla diya hai, ab mere ikhtiyar mein woh cheez hai nahi jis ke liye tum jaldi macha rahay ho, faisla ka sara ikhtiyar Allah ko hai, wohi amar haq bayan karta hai aur wohi behtareen faisla karne wala hai"
  6,58,"kaho, agar kahin woh cheez mere ikhtiyar mein hoti jis ki tum jaldi macha rahay ho to mere aur tumahray darmain kabhi ka faisla ho chuka hota magar Allah ziyada behtar jaanta hai ke zaalmon ke sath kya maamla kya jana chahiye"
  6,59,usi ke paas ghaib ki knjyan hain jinhein is ke siwa koi nahi jaanta behar o Bar mein jo kuch hai sab se woh waaqif hai darakht se girnay wala koi pata aisa nahi jis ka usay ilm nah ho zameen ke tareek pardon mein koi dana aisa nahi jis se woh bakhabar nah ho khushk o tarsab kuch aik khuli kitaab mein likha howa hai
  6,60,"wohi hai jo raat ko tumhari roohein qabz karta hai aur din ko jo kuch tum karte ho usay jaanta hai, phir dosray roz woh tumhe isi kaarobar ke aalam mein wapas bhaij deta hai taakay zindagi ki muqarrar muddat poori ho aakhir-kaar isi ki taraf tumhari wapsi hai, phir o hay tumhe bta day ga ke tum kya karte rahay ho"
  6,61,"apne bundon par woh poori qudrat rakhta hai aur tum par nigrani karne walay muqarrar kar ke bhejta hai, yahan taq ke jab tum mein se kisi ki mout ka waqt aa jata hai to is ke beje hue farishtay is ki jaan nikaal letay hain aur apna farz injaam dainay mein zara kotahi nahi karte"
  6,62,"phir sab ke sab Allah , apne haqeeqi aaqa ki taraf wapas laaye jatay hain khabardaar ho jao, faisla ke saaray ikhtiyarat isi ko haasil hain aur woh hisaab lainay mein bohat taiz hai"
  6,63,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! a noon se pucho, sehraa aur samandar ki tarikeon mein kon tumhe khatraat se bachata hai? ko noon hai jis se tum ( museebat ke waqt ) gur gara, girgira kar aur chupkay chupkay duayen mangte ho? kis se kehte ho ke agar is bulaa se to ne hum ko bacha liya to hum zaroor shukar guzaar hon ge ?"
  6,64,"kaho, Allah tumhe uss se aur har takleef se nijaat deta hai phir tum dosaron ko uss ka shareektehra-tay ho"
  6,65,"kaho, woh iss par Qadir hai ke tum par koi azaab oopar se nazil kar day, ya tumahray qadmon ke neechay se barpaa kar day, ya tumhe garohoon mein taqseem kar ke aik giroh ko dosray giroh ki taaqat ka maza chukhwaday dekho, hum kis terhan baar baar mukhtalif tareeqon se apni nishanain un ke samnay paish kar rahay hain shayad ke yeh haqeeqat ko samajh len"
  6,66,tumhari qoum uss ka inkaar kar rahi hai halaank woh haqeeqat hai inn se keh do ke mein tum par hawala daar nahi banaya gaya hon
  6,67,"har khabar ke zahuur mein anay ka aik waqt muqarrar hai, anqareeb tum ko khud injaam maloom ho jaye ga"
  6,68,aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! jab tum dekho ke log hamari ayaat par nuqta chainian kar rahay hain to un ke paas se hatt jao yahan taq ke woh is guftagu ko chore kar doosri baton mein lag jayen aur agar kabhi shetan tumhe behlaway mein daal day to jis waqt tumhe is ghalti ka ehsas ho jaye is ke baad phir aisay zalim logon ke paas nah betho
  6,69,"unn ke hisaab mein se kisi cheez ki zimma daari parhaiz gaar logon par nahi hai, Albata nasiyaat karna unn ka farz hai shayad ke woh ghalat rawi se bach jayen"
  6,70,"chhorro unn logon ko jinhon ne apne deen ko khail aur tamasha bana rakha hai aur jinhein duniya ki zindagi fraib mein mubtala kiye hue hai haan magar yeh quran suna kar nasiyaat aur tanbeeh karte raho ke kahin koi shakhs apne kiye krtoton ke wabaal mein girftar nah ho jaye, aur girftar bhi iss haal mein ho ke Allah se bachanay wala koi haami o madad gaar aur koi safarishi is ke liye nah ho, aur gir woh har mumkin cheez Fidya mein day kar chhotna chahay to woh bhi is se qubool nah ki jaye, kyunkay aisay log to khud apni kamaai ke nateeja mein pakdae jayen ge, un ko to apne inkaar haq ke muawza mein kholta howa pani peenay ko aur dard naak azaab bhgtne ko miley ga"
  6,71,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se po chhoo kya hum Allah ko chore kar unn ko pukaarain jo nah hamein naffa day satke hain nah nuqsaan? aur jabkay Allah hamein seedha rasta dikha chuka hai to kya ab hum ultay paon phir jayen? kya hum apna haal uss shakhs ka sa kar len jisay shaitano ne sehraa mein bhatka diya ho aur woh heran o srgrdan phir raha hodar-aa-nhala-n keh is ke saathi usay pukaar rahay hon ke idher aa yeh seedhi raah mojood hai? kaho, haqeeqat mein sahih rahnumai to sirf Allah hi ki rahnumai hai aur is ki taraf se hamein yeh hukum mila hai ke maalik kaayenaat ke agay sir itaat khham kar do"
  6,72,"namaz qaim karo aur is ki nafarmani se bachcho, isi ki taraf tum samete jao ge"
  6,73,"wohi hai jis ne aasman o zameen ko Bar haq peda kya hai aur jis daal noon woh kahe ga ke hashar ho jaye isi din woh ho jaye ga is ka irshad ain haq hai aur jis roz sor phonka jaayegaa is roz basshahi usi ki hogi, woh ghaib aur shahadat har cheez ka aalam hai aur Dana aur bakhabar hai"
  6,74,"ibrahim ka waqea yaad karo jabkay uss ne apne baap Azar se kaha tha"" kya to buton ko khuda banata hai? mein to tujhe aur teri qoum ko khuli gumraahi mein paata hon """
  6,75,ibrahim ko hum isi terhan zameen aur asmano ka nizaam saltanat dikhata thay aur is liye dikhata thay ke woh yaqeen karne walon mein se ho jaye
  6,76,chunancha jab raat is par taari hui to uss ne aik taar a dekha kaha yeh mera rab hai magar jab woh doob gaya to bola doob jaane walon ka to mein garweedah nahi hon
  6,77,phir jab chaand chamakta nazar aaya to kaha yeh hai mera rab magar jab woh bhi doob gaya to kaha agar mere rab ne Meer y rahnumai nah ki hoti to mein bhi gumraah logon mein shaamil ho gaya hota
  6,78,"phir jab Sooraj ko roshan dekha to kaha yeh hai mera rab, yeh sab se bara hai magar jab woh bhi dooba to ibrahim pukaar utha"" ae baradran qoum! mein unn sab se bezaar hon jinhein tum khuda ka shareektehra-tay ho"
  6,79,"mein neto yaksuho kar apna rukh uss hasti ki taraf kar liya jis ne zameen aur asmano ko peda kya hai aur mein hargiz shirk karne walon mein se nahi hon """
  6,80,"is ki qoum is se jhagrnay lagi to is ne qoum se kaha"" kya tum log Allah ke maamla mein mujh se jhagarte ho? halaank is ne mujhe raah raast dikha di hai aur mein tumahray tehra-ay hue sharikon se nahi darta, haan agar mera rab kuch chahay to woh zaroor ho sakta hai mere rab ka ilm har cheez par chaaya howa hai, phir kya tum hosh mein nah aao ge ?"
  6,81,aur aakhir mein tumahray tehra-ay hue sharikon se kaisay dron jabkay tum Allah ke sath un cheezon ko khudai mein shareek banatay hue nahi drtay jin ke liye is ne tum par koi sanad nazil nahi ki hai? hum dono fareeqon mein se kon ziyada be khofi o itminan ka mustahiq hai? batao agar tum kuch ilm rakhtay ho
  6,82,"haqeeqat mein to aman unhi ke liye hai aur raah raast par wohi hain jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne apne imaan ko zulm ke sath aaloda nahi kya """
  6,83,yeh thi hamari woh Hujjat jo hum ne ibrahim ko is ki qoum ke muqaabla mein ataa ki hum jisay chahtay hain buland martabay ataa karte hain haq yeh hai ke tumhara rab nihayat Dana aur Aleem hai
  6,84,"phir hum ne ibrahim ko ishaq aur yaqoob jaisi aulaad di aur har aik ko raah raast dikhayi ( wohi raah raast jo ) is se pehlay Nooh ko dikhayi thi aur usi ki nasal se hum ne DAWOD, sulaiman, ayub, yousuf, moose aur haroon ko ( hadaayat bakhsh ) iss terhan hum naiko karon ko un ki neki ka badla dete hain"
  6,85,"( usi ki aulaad se ) Zikria, yahya, eesa aur ilyas ko ( raah yab kya ) har aik un mein se Saleh tha"
  6,86,"( isi ke khandan se ) Ismael,Yasa'a , aur Younis aur loot ko ( rasta dekhaya ) inn mein se har aik ko hum ne tamam duniya walon par fazeelat ataa ki"
  6,87,"neez un ke aaba o ajdaad aur un ki aulaad aur un ke bhai bundon mein se bahuton ko hum ne nawaza, inhen apni khidmat ke liye chunn liya aur seedhay rastay ki taraf unn ki rahnumai ki"
  6,88,yeh Allah ki hadaayat hai jis ke sath woh apne bundon mein se jis ki chahta hai rahnumai karta hai lekin agar kahin un logon ne shirk kya hota to un ka sab kya karaya ghaarat ho jata
  6,89,woh log thay jin ko hum ne kitaab aur hukum aur nabuwat ataa ki thi ab agar yeh log is ko maan-ne se inkaar karte hain to ( parwa nahi ) hum ne kuch aur logon ko yeh Nemat saump di hai jo is se munkir nahi hain
  6,90,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! wohi log Allah ki taraf se hadaayat Yafta thay, unhi ke rasta par tum chalo, aur keh do ke mein ( is tableegh o hadaayat ke ) kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi hon, yeh to aik aam nasiyaat hai tamam duniya walon ke liye"
  6,91,"un logon ne Allah ka bohat ghalat andaza lagaya jab kaha ke Allah ne kisi bashar par kuch nazil nahi kya hai un se pucho, phir woh kitaab jisay moose laya tha, jo tamam insanon ke liye roshni aur hadaayat thi, jisay tum Parah Parah kar ke rakhtay ho, kuch dikhata ho aur bohat kuch chhupa jatay ho, aur jis ke zareya se tum ko woh ilm diya gaya jo nah tumhe haasil tha aur nah tumahray baap dada ko, aakhir uss ka nazil karne wala kon tha? bas itna keh do ke Allah , phir unhen apni Daleel bazyon se khailnay ke liye chore do"
  6,92,( usi kitaab ki terhan ) yeh aik kitaab hai jisay hum ne nazil kya hai barri kher o barket wali hai uss cheez ki tasdeeq karti hai jo is se pehlay aayi thi aur is liye nazil ki gayi hai ke is ke zareya se tum bustiyon ke iss markaz ( yani mecca ) aur is ke atraaf mein rehne walon ko mutnabba karo jo lau g akhirat ko mantay hain woh is kitaab par imaan laatay hain aur un ka haal yeh hai ke apni namazon ki pabandi karte hain
  6,93,"aur uss shakhs se bara zalim aur kon hoga jo Allah par jhoota bohtan gharrey, ya kahe ke mujh par wahi aayi haidar-aa-n hala-n kehہ is par koi wahi nazil nah ki gayi ho, ya jo Allah ki nazil kardah cheez ke muqaabla mein kahe ke mein bhi aisi cheez nazil kar ke dikha dun ga? kash tum zaalmon ko is haalat mein dekh sakuu jab ke woh sukrat -e- mout mein dubkian kha rahay hotay hain aur farishtay haath barha barha kar keh rahay hotay hain ke"" lao, nikalu apni jaan, aaj tumhe unn baton ki Padaash mein zillat ka azaab diya jaye ga jo tum Allah par tohmat rakh kar na-haq bakka karte thay aur uss ki ayaat ke muqaabla mein sar kashi dikhata thay """
  6,94,"( aur Allah farmaiye ga )"" lau ab tum waisay hi tan tanha hamaray samnay haazir hogaye jaissa hum ne tumhe pehli martaba akela peda kya tha, jo kuch hum ne tumhe duniya mein diya tha woh sab tum peechay chore aeye ho, aur ab hum tumahray sath tumahray unn safarshiyun ko bhi nahi dekhte jin ke mutaliq tum samajte thay ke tumahray kaam bananay mein un ka bhi kuch hissa hai, tumahray aapas ke sab raabtey toot gay aur woh sab tum se gum hogaye jin ka tum zeam rakhtay thay """
  6,95,"danay aur ghuthli ko pharnay wala Allah hai wohi zindah ko murda se nkalta hai aur wohi murda ko zindah se kharij karta hai yeh saaray kaam karne wala Allah hai, phir tum kidhar behke chalay ja rahay ho ?"
  6,96,parda shab ko chaak kar ke wohi subah nkalta hai usi ne raat ko sukoon ka waqt banaya hai usi ne chaand aur Sooraj ke tulu o ghuroob ka hisaab muqarrar kya hai yeh sab usi zabardast qudrat aur ilm rakhnay walay ke tehra-ay hue andazay hain
  6,97,aur wohi hai jis ne tumahray liye taron ko sehraa aur samandar ki tarikeon mein rasta maloom karne ka zareya banaya dekho hum ne nishanain khol kar bayan kar di hain unn logon ke liye jo ilm rakhtay hain
  6,98,aur wohi hai jis ne aik mutnaqas se tum ko peed a kya phir har aik ke liye aik jaye qarar hai aur aik is ke sonpe jaane ki jagah yeh nishanain hum ne wazeh kar di hain unn logon ke liye jo samajh boojh rakhtay hain
  6,99,"aur wohi hai jis ne aasman se pani barsaya, phir is ke zareya se har qisam ki nabataat ugai, phir is se harey harey khait aur darakht peda kiye, phir un se teh bah teh charrhey hue danay nikalay aur khajoor ke shagoofon se phalon ke guchay ke guchay peda kiye jo boojh ke maaray jhuke parte hain, aur angoor, Zaitoon aur aanar ke baagh lagaye jin ke phal aik dosray se mlitay jaltay bhi hain aur phir unn ke paknay ki kefiyat zara ghhor ki nazar se dekho, inn cheezon mein nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo imaan laatay hain"
  6,100,"iss par bhi logon ne junoo ko Allah ka shareektehra diya, halaank woh unn ka khaaliq hai, aur be jaane boojhay is ke liye betay aur betiyan tasneef kar den, halaank woh pak aur baala tar hai unn baton se jo yeh log kehte hain"
  6,101,woh to asmano aur zameen ka mo-jad hai is ka koi beta kaisay ho sakta hai jabkay koi is ki shareek zindagi hi nahi hai is ne har cheez ko peda kya hai aur woh har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai
  6,102,"yeh hai Allah tumhara rab, koi khuda is ke siwa nahi hai, har cheez ka khaaliq, lehaza tum isi ki bandagi karo aur woh har cheez ka kafeel hai"
  6,103,"nigehain is ko nahi pa sakteen aur woh nigahon ko pa laita hai, woh nihayat bareek been aur bakhabar hai"
  6,104,"dekho, tumahray paas tumahray rab ki taraf se baseerat ki roshniyan aa gayi hain, ab jo benaye se kaam le ga apna hi bhala kere ga aur jo andha banay ga khud nuqsaan uthaye ga, mein tum par koi Pasban nahi hon"
  6,105,"iss terhan hum apni ayaat ko baar baar mukhtalif tareeqon se bayan karte hain aur is liye karte hain ke yeh log kahin tum kisi se parh aeye ho, aur jo log ilm rakhtay hain un par hum haqeeqat ko roshan kar den"
  6,106,ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! uss wahi ki pairwi kiye jao jo tum par tumahray rab ki taraf se nazil hui hai kyunkay uss aik rab ke siwa koi aur khuda nahi hai aur un mushriqeen ke peechay nah parro
  6,107,agar Allah ki Mushiyat hoti to ( woh khud aisa bandobast karsaktha tha ke ) yeh log shirk nah karte tum ko hum ne un par Pasban muqarrar nahi kya hai aur nah tum un par hawala daar ho
  6,108,"aur ( ae imaan laane walo! ) yeh log Allah ke siwa jin ko pkarte hain inhen gaaliyan nah do, kahin aisa nah ho ke yeh shirk se agay barh kar jahalat ki bana par Allah ko gaaliyan dainay lagen hum ne isi terhan har giroh ke liye is ke amal ko khushnuma bana diya hai phir inhen apne rab hi ki taraf palat kar aana hai, uss waqt woh unhen bta day ga ke woh kya karte rahay hain"
  6,109,"yeh log kari kari kasmain kha kha kar kehte hain ke agar koi nishani hamaray samnay aa jaye to hum is par imaan le ayen ge ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho ke"" nishanain to Allah ke paas hain"" aur tumhe kaisay samjhaya jaye ke agar nishanain aa bhi jayen to yeh imaan laane walay nahi"
  6,110,hum usi terhan un ke dilon aur nigahon ko phair rahay hain jis terhan yeh pehli martaba is par imaan nahi laaye thay hum inhen un ki sar kashi hi mein bhatakne ke liye chhorey dete hain
  6,111,"agar hum farishtay bhi un par nazil kar dete aur murdy un se baatein karte aur duniya bhar ki cheezon ko hum un ki aankhon ke samnay jama kar dete tab bhi yeh imaan laane walay nah thay, ila yeh ke Mushiyat Ellahi yahi ho ke woh imaan layein, magar aksar log nadani ki baatein karte hain"
  6,112,aur hum ne to isi terhan hamesha shetan insanon aur shetan junoo ko har nabi ka dushman banaya hai jo aik dosray par khush aaynd baatein dhokay aur fraib ke tor par alqa karte rahay hain agar tumahray rab ki Mushiyat yeh hoti ke woh aisa nah karen to woh kabhi nah karte pas tum unhen un ke haal par chore do ke apni aftara pardadiyan karte rahen
  6,113,( yeh sab kuch hum inhen isi liye karne day rahay hain ke ) jo log akhirat par imaan nahi rakhtay unn ke dil iss ( khushnuma dhokay ) ki taraf mael hon aur woh is se raazi ho jayen aur unn buraiyon ka Iktisab karen jin ka Iktisab woh karna chahtay hain
  6,114,"phir jab haal yeh hai to kya mein Allah ke siwa koi aur faisla karne wala talaash karoon, halaank is ne poori tafseel ke sath tumhari taraf kitaab nazil kar di hai? aur jin logon ko hum ne ( tum se pehlay ) kitaab di thi woh jantay hain ke yeh kitaab tumahray rab hi ki taraf se haq ke sath nazil hui hai lehaza tum shak karne walon mein shaamil nah ho"
  6,115,"tumahray rab ki baat sachaai aur insaaf ke aitbaar se kaamil hai, koi is ke Faramin ko tabdeel karne wala nahi hai aur woh sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
  6,116,aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! agar tum unn logon ki aksariyat ke kehnay par chalo jo zameen mein baste hain to woh tumhe Allah ke rasta se bhatka den ge woh to mehez gumaan par chaltay aur qiyaas aarayyan karte hain
  6,117,Dur haqeeqat tumhara rab ziyada behtar jaanta hai ke kon uss ke rastay se hata howa hai aur kon seedhi raah par hai
  6,118,phir agar tum log Allah ki ayaat par imaan rakhtay ho to jis janwar par Allah ka naam liya gaya ho uss ka gosht khao
  6,119,"aakhir kya wajah hai ke tum woh cheez nah khao jis par Allah ka naam liya gaya ho, halaank jin cheezon ka istemaal haalat iztarar ke siwa doosri tamam halaton mein Allah ne haraam kar diya hai unn ki tafseel woh tumhe bta chuka hai bakasrat logon ka haal yeh hai ke ilm ke baghair mehez apni khwahisaat ki bana par gumraah kin baatein karte hain, un hadd se guzarnay walon ko tumhara rab khoob jaanta hai"
  6,120,"tum khulay gunaaho se bhi bachcho aur chupay gunaaho se bhi, jo log gunah ka Iktisab karte hain woh apni is kamaai ka badla paker rahen ge"
  6,121,"aur jis janwar ko Allah ka naam le kar zibah nah kya gaya ho is ka gosht nah khao, aisa karna fisq hai shyatin apne sathiyon ke dilon mein shukook o aitrazaat alqa karte hain taakay woh tum se jhagra karen lekin agar tum ne unn ki itaat qubool kar li to yaqeenan tum mushriq ho"
  6,122,kya woh shakhs jo pehlay murda tha phir hum ne usay zindagi bakhsh aur is ko woh roshni ataa ki jis ke ujalay mein woh logon ke darmain zindagi ki raah tey karta hai uss shakhs ki terhan ho sakta hai jo tarikeon mein para howa ho aur kisi terhan unn se nah nikalta ho? kafiroon ke liye to isi terhan un ke aamaal khushnuma bana diye gay hain
  6,123,"aur isi terhan hum ne har bastii mein is ke barray barray mujrimon ko laga diya hai ke wahan apne makr o fraib ka jaal philayin darasal woh apne fraib ke jaal mein aap phnste hain, magar unhen is ka shaoor nahi hai"
  6,124,"jab un ke samnay koi aayat aati hai to woh kehte hain"" hum nah manen ge jab taq ke woh cheez khud hum ko nah di jaye jo Allah ke Rasolo-n ko di gayi hai"" Allah ziyada behtar jaanta hai ke apni peghambari ka kaam kis se le aur kis terhan le qareeb hai woh waqt jab yeh mujrim apni mkaryon ki Padaash mein Allah ke haan zillat aur sakht azaab se do chaar hon ge"
  6,125,pas ( yeh haqeeqat hai ke ) jisay Allah hadaayat bakhsnay ka iradah karta hai uss ka seenah islam ke liye khol deta hai aur jisay gumraahi mein daalnay ka iradah karta hai uss ke seenay ko tang kar deta hai aur aisa bhinchtahai ke ( islam ka tasawwur karte hi ) ussay yun maloom honay lagta hai ke goya is ki rooh aasman ki taraf parwaaz kar rahi hai iss terhan Allah ( haq se faraar aur nafrat ki ) napaaki unn logon par musallat kar deta hai jo imaan nahi laatay
  6,126,halaank yeh rasta tumahray rab ka seedha rasta hai aur is ke nishanaat unn logon ke liye wazeh kar diye gay hain jo nasiyaat qubool karte hain
  6,127,unn keliye unn ke rab ke paas salamti ka ghar hai aur woh un ka sir parast hai uss sahih tarz amal ki wajah se jo unhon ne ikhtiyar kya
  6,128,"jis roz Allah un sab logon ko ghair kar jama kere ga, is roz woh junoo se khitaab kar ke farmaiye ga ke"" a y giroh jin! tum ne noo insani par khoob haath saaf kya"" insanon mein se jo unn ke Rafeeq thay woh arz karen ge"" parvar-digaar! hum mein se har aik ne dosray ko khoo bay istemaal kya hai, aur ab hum uss waqt par aa puhanche hain jo to ne hamaray liye muqarrar kar diya tha"" Allah farmaiye ga"" acha ab aag tumhara thikana hai, is mein tum hamesha raho ge"" a"" seen se bachchen ge sirf wohi jinhein Allah bachana chahay ga, be shak tumhara rab Dana aur Aleem hai"
  6,129,"dekho, is terhan hum ( aakhir t- mein ) zaalmon ko aik dosray ka saathi banayen ge uss kamaai ki wajah se jo woh ( duniya mein aik dosray ke sath mil kar ) karte thay"
  6,130,"( is mauqa par Allah un se pouchye ga ke )"" ae giroh jin o ins, kya tumahray paas khud tum hi mein se woh paighambar nahi aeye thay jo tum ko meri ayaat sunaate aur iss din ke injaam se darate thay ?"" woh kahin ge"" haan, hum apne khilaaf khud gawahi dete hain"" aaj duniya ki zindagi ne inn logon ko dhokay mein daal rakha hai, magar uss waqt woh khud apne khilaaf gawahi den ge ke woh kafir thay"
  6,131,( yeh shahadat unn se is liye li jaye gi ke yeh saabit ho jaye ke ) tumhara rab bustiyon ko zulm ke sath tabah karne wala nah tha jabkay un ke bashinday haqeeqat se na waaqif hon
  6,132,har shakhs ka darja uss ke amal ke lehaaz se hai aur tumhara rab logon ke aamaal se be khabar nahi hai
  6,133,tumhara rab be niaz hai aur meharbani is ka Shewa hai agar o hay chahay to tum logon ko le jaye aur tumhari jagah dosray jin logon ko chahay le aeye jis terhan uss ne tumhe kuch aur logon ki nasal se uthaya hai
  6,134,tum se jis cheez ka wada kya ja raha hai woh yaqeenan anay wali hai aur tum khuda ko aajiz kar dainay ki taaqat nahi rakhtay
  6,135,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! keh do ke logo! tum apni jagah amal karte raho aur mein bhi apni jagah amal kar raha hon, anqareeb tumhe maloom ho jaye ga ke injaam car kis ke haq mein behtar hota hai, bahar haal yeh haqeeqat hai ke zalim kabhi Falah nahi pa satke"
  6,136,"inn logon ne Allah ke liye khud usi ki peda ki hui kheetion aur maweshion mein se aik hissa muqarrar kya hai aur kehte hain yeh Allah ke liye hai, bzam khud, aur yeh hamaray tehra-ay hue sharikon ke liye phir jo hissa un ke tehra-ay hue sharikon ke liye hai woh to Allah ko nahi pohanchana magar jo Allah ke liye hai woh un ke sharikon ko poanch jata hai kaisay buray faislay karte hain yeh log !"
  6,137,"aur isi terhan bohat se mushrikon ke liye un ke sharikon ne apni aulaad ke qatal ko khushnuma bana diya hai taakay un ko halakat mein mubtala karen aur un par un ke deen ko mushtaba bana den agar Allah chahta to yeh aisa nah karte, lehaza inhen chore do ke apni aftara pardaaz yun mein lagey rahen"
  6,138,"kehte hain yeh janwar aur yeh khait mehfooz hain, a nahi sirf wohi log kha satke hain jinhein hum khilana chahain, halaank yeh pabandi un ki khud sakhta hai phir kuch janwar hain jin par sawari aur baar bardari haraam kar di gayi hai aur kuch janwar hain jin par Allah ka naam nahi letay, aur yeh sab kuch unhon ne Allah par aftara kya hai, anqareeb Allah inhen un aftara pardaaz yun ka badla day ga"
  6,139,"aur kehte hain ke jo kuch un janwaron ke pait mein hai yeh hamaray mardon ke liye makhsoos hai aur hamari aurton par haraam, lekin agar woh murda ho to dono is ke khanay mein shareek ho satke hain yeh baatein jo unhon ne ghurr li hain un ka badla Allah inhen day kar rahay ga yaqeenan woh hakeem hai aur sab baton ki usay khabar hai"
  6,140,yaqeenan khasaray mein par gay woh log jinhon ne apni aulaad ko jahalat o nadani ki bana par qatal kya aur Allah ke diye hue rizaq ko Allah par aftara pardazi kar ke haraamtehra liya yaqeenan woh bhatak gay aur hargiz woh raah raast panay walon mein se nah thay
  6,141,"woh Allah hi hai jis ne terhan terhan ke baagh aur takistaanaur nakhlistan peda kiye, khatiyan agayin jin se qisam qisam ke makolaat haasil hotay hain, Zaitoon aur aanar ke darakht peda kiye jin ke phal soorat mein mushaba aur mazay mein mukhtalif hotay hain khao un ki pedawar jab ke yeh phalay-n, aur Allah ka haq ada karo jab is ki fasal katu, aur hadd se nah guzro ke Allah hadd se guzarnay walon ko pasand nahi karta"
  6,142,phir wohi hai jis ne maweshion mein se woh janwar bhi peda kiye jin se sawari o baar bardari ka kaam liya jata hai aur woh bhi jo khanay aur bichenay ke kaam atay hain khao unn cheezon mein se jo Allah ne tumhe bakhsh hain aur shetan ki pairo y nah karo ke woh tumhara khula dushman hai
  6,143,"yeh aath nar o madah hain, do bheer ki qisam se aur do bakri ki qisam se, ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se pucho ke Allah ne unn ke nar haraam kiye hain ya madah, ya woh bachay jo bheiron aur bakrion ke pait mein hon? theek theek ilm ke sath mujhe batao agar tum sachey ho"
  6,144,"aur isi terhan do oont ki qisam se hain aur do gaaye ki qisam se pucho, inn ke nar Allah ne haraam kiye hain ya madah, ya woh bachay jo oontni aur gaaye ke pait mein hon? kya tum uss waqt haazir thay jab Allah ne un ke haraam honay ka hukum tumhe diya tha? phir uss shakhs se barh kar zalim aur kon hoga jo Allah ki taraf mansoob kar ke jhooti baat kahe taakay ilm ke baghair logon ki ghalat raah namai kere yaqeenan Allah aisay zaalmon ko raah raast nahi dekhata"
  6,145,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho ke jo wahi tumahray paas aayi hai is mein to mein koi cheez aisi nahi paata jo kisi khanay walay par haraam ho, ila yeh ke woh Murdaar ho, ya bahaya howa khoon ho, ya suar ka gosht ho ke woh napak hai, ya fisq ho ke Allah ke siwa kisi aur ke naam par zibah kya gaya ho phir jo shakhs majaboori ki haalat mein ( koi cheez inn mein se kha le ) baghair is ke ke woh nafarmani ka iradah rakhta ho aur baghair is ke ke woh hadd zaroorat se tajawaz kere, to yaqeenan tumhara rab Dur guzar se kaam lainay wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  6,146,"aur jin logon ne yahoodiyat ikhtiyar ki un par hum ne sab naakhun walay janwar haraam kar diye thay, aur gaaye aur bakri ki charbi bhi bajuz uss ke jo unn ki peeth ya unn ki anton se lagi hui ho ya haddi se lagi reh jaye yeh hum ne un ki sar kashi ki saza unhen di thi aur yeh jo kuch hum keh rahay hain bilkul sach keh rahay hain"
  6,147,ab agar woh tumhejjhutlainto un se keh do ke tumahray rab ka daman rehmat wasee hai aur mujrimon se is ke azaab ko phera nahi ja sakta
  6,148,"yeh mushriq log ( tumhari un baton ke jawab mein ) zaroor kahin ge ke"" agar Allah chahta to nah hum shirk karte aur nah hamaray baap dada, aur nah hum kisi cheez ko haraam thrate"" aisi hi baatein bana bana kar inn se pehlay ke logon ne bhi jhtlaya tha yahan taq ke aakhir-kaar hamaray azaab ka maza unhon ne chakh liya un se kaho"" kya tumahray paas koi ilm hai jisay hamaray samnay paish krsko? tum to mehez gumaan par chal rahay ho aur nari qiyaas aarayyan karte ho """
  6,149,"phir kaho ( tumhari is Hujjat ke muqaabla mein )"" haqeeqat ras Hujjat to Allah ke paas hai, be shak agar Allah chahta to tum sab ko hadaayat day deta """
  6,150,"un se kaho ke"" lao apne woh gawah jo is baat ki shahadat den ke Allah hi ne inn cheezon ko haraam kya hai"" phir agar woh shahadat day den to tum un ke sath shahadat nah dena, aur hargiz unn logon ki khwahisaat ke peechay nah chalna jinhon ne hamari ayaat ko jhtlaya hai, aur jo akhirat ke munkir hain, aur jo dosaron ko apne rab ka humsar banatay hain"
  6,151,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho ke aao mein tumhe sunaoon tumahray rab ne tum par kya pabandiyan aed ki hain : yeh ke is ke sath kisi ko shareek nah karo, aur walidain ke sath naik sulooq karo, aur apni aulaad ko muflisi ke dar se qatal nah karo, hum tumhe bhi rizaq dete hain aur a noon ko bhi den ge aur be sharmi ki baton ke qareeb bhi nah jao khuwa woh khuli hon ya chhupi aur kisi jaan ko jisay Allah ne mohtaramTehraya hai halaak nah karo magar haq ke sath yeh baatein hain jin ki hadaayat is ne tumhe ki hai, shayad ke tum samajh boojh se kaam lau"
  6,152,"aur yeh ke yateem ke maal ke qareeb nah jao magar aisay tareeqa se jo behtareen ho, yahan taq ke woh apne sun Rashd ko poanch jaye aur naap toal mein poora insaaf karo, hum har shakhs par zimma daari ka itna hi baar rakhtay hain jitna is ke imkaan mein hai, aur jab baat kaho insaaf ki kaho khuwa maamla apne rishta daar hi ka kyun nah ho, aur Allah ke ehad ko poora karo un baton ki hadaayat Allah ne tumhe ki hai shayad ke tum nasiyaat qubool karo"
  6,153,"neez is ki hadaayat yeh hai ke yahi mera seedha rasta hai lehaza tum isi par chalo aur dosray raastoon par nah chalo ke woh is ke rastay se hata kar tumhe paragandah kar den ge yeh hai woh hadaayat jo tumahray rab ne tumhe ki hai, shayad ke tum kaj rawi se bachcho"
  6,154,phir hum ne moose ko kitaab ataa ki thi jo bhalai ki rawish ikhtiyar karne walay ensaan par Nemat ki takmeel aur har zurori cheez ki tafseel aur sara sar hadaayat aur rehmat thi ( aur is liye bani Israel ko di gayi thi ke ) shayad log apne rab ki mulaqaat par imaan layein
  6,155,"aur isi terhan yeh kitaab hum ne nazil ki hai, aik barket wali kitaab pas tum iss ki pairwi karo aur taqwa ki rawish ikhtiyar karo, baeed nahi ke tum par reham kya jaye"
  6,156,"ab tum yeh nahi keh satke ke kitaab to hum se pehlay ke do garohoon ko di gayi thi, aur hum ko kuch khabar nah thi ke woh kya parhte parhatay thay"
  6,157,"aur ab tum yeh bahana bhi nahi kar saktay ke agar hum par kitaab nazil ki gayi hoti to hum un se ziyada raast ro saabit hotay tumahray paas tumahray rab ki taraf se aik Daleel roshan aur hadaayat aur rehmat aa gayi hai, ab is se barh kar zalim kon hoga jo Allah ki ayaat kojhutla-ay aur un se mun moray jo log hamari ayaat se mun morty hain inhen is ro gardani ki Padaash mein hum bad tareen saza day kar rahen ge"
  6,158,"kya ab log is ke muntazir hain ke un ke samnay farishtay aa kharray hon, ya tumhara rab khud aa jaye, ya tumahray rab ki baaz Sarih nishanain namodaar ho jayen? jis roz tumahray rab ki baaz makhsoos nishanain namodaar ho jayen gi phir kisi aisay shakhs ko is ka imaan kuch faida nah day ga jo pehlay imaan nah laya ho ya jis ne apne imaan mein koi bhalai nah kamaai ho ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se keh do ke acha, tum intzaar karo, hum bhi intzaar karte hain"
  6,159,"jin logon ne apne deen ko tukre tukre kar diya aur giroh giroh ban gay yaqeenan un se tumhara kuch vaastaa nahi, un ka maamla to Allah ke supurd hai, wohi un ko betaye ga ke unhon ne kya kuch kya hai"
  6,160,"jo Allah ke huzoor neki le kar aeye ga is ke liye das gina ajar hai, aur jo badi le kar aeye ga is ko itna hi badla diya jaye ga jitna is ne qasoor kya hai, aur kisi par zulm nah kya jaye ga"
  6,161,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! kaho mere rab ne bilyaqeen mujhe seedha rasta dikha diya hai, bilkul theek deen jis mein koi theerh nahi, ibrahim ka tareeqa jisay yaksu ho kar uss ne ikhtiyar kya tha aur woh mushrikon mein se nah tha"
  6,162,"kaho, meri namaz, mere tamam marasim abodit, mera jeena aur mera marna, sab kuch Allah rab alaalmin ke liye hai"
  6,163,jis ka koi shareek nahi isi ka mujhe hukum diya gaya hai aur sab se pehlay sir itaat jhukanay wala mein hon
  6,164,"kaho, kya mein Allah ke siwa koi aur rab talaash karoon halan ke wohi har cheez ka rab hai? har shakhs jo kuch kamata hai is ka zimma daar woh khud hai, koi boojh uthany wala dosray ka boojh nahi uthata, phir tum sab ko apne rab ki taraf palatna hai, uss waqt woh tumahray ikhtilafat ki haqeeqat tum par khol day ga"
  6,165,"wohi hai jis ne tum ko zameen ka khalifa banaya, aur tum mein se baaz ko baaz ke muqaabla mein ziyada buland darjay diye, taakay jo kuch tum ko diya hai isi mein tumhari azmaish kere be shak tumhara rab saza dainay mein bhi bohat taiz hai aur bohat dar guzar karne aur reham frmane wala bhi hai"
